The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method is a deep learning-based approach, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Additionally, the paper introduces a new similarity metric for multi-label images, which involves quantifying the similarity between instances, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
